Class GetKodAktualnihoUtvaruAsyncTask

  • java.lang.Object
      • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.client.RetainedAsyncTask<UtvarKodANazev>
        • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.client.GetKodAktualnihoUtvaruAsyncTask

  • public class GetKodAktualnihoUtvaruAsyncTask
extends RetainedAsyncTask<UtvarKodANazev>
    GetKodAktualnihoUtvaruAsyncTask is a an async task class for the department code and name loading.

    This is a subclass of RetainedAsyncTask specialized on retrieving the UtvarKodANazev. UtvarKodANazev is a class holding the information about a department code and name.

    As well as in GetCrimeDataTask, this class retrieves the data using the same concept of "method call URL". For the details about the method call URLs creation and usage see GetCrimeDataTask.

    See Also:
    UtvarKodANazev, RetainedAsyncTask, GetCrimeDataTask
